{"tid":1350087,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《新華社》批曼城傲慢不尊重中國","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:13:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"015ed497dfc20c53c1970e1fe028aee87f7d51a3","tid":1350087,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼城剛剛完成分別在上海與南京舉行的英超挑戰盃，現已到達香港將跟傑志進行友賽。中國媒體《新華社》在英文官網發文，抨擊藍月在中國的活動只顧賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n曼城在今次中國之行可說是災難多多，先是遇上兩次航班取消的問題，令阻礙了球隊的行程，更在英超挑戰盃決賽以互射12碼不敵狼隊，失落冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》在賽後於英文官網發表文章，批評曼城在出戰英超挑戰盃時，沒有照顧到中國球迷的需要，批評他們沒有對中國傳媒與一眾球迷給予足夠的尊重。文章更點名指責領隊哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）沒有主動為球迷簽名。<br />\n<br />\n文章寫道，「作為英超冠軍，他們在中國友賽只是為了商業，沒有熱情，忽視了球迷的要求；其他球會為球迷服務，但曼城只是為了賺中國球迷的錢。同時，他們覺得自己是英超挑戰盃的貴賓，出現這種傲慢的態度與信念，令他們與其他有份出席的球會形成鮮明對比。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"61c498afd50094a431c064b77f9bd0f205ac305c","tid":1350087,"uid":16659,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11664710.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200b/MAIN-Premier-League-Manchester-City-vs-West-Ham-United.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11664710.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1200b%2FMAIN-Premier-League-Manchester-City-vs-West-Ham-United.jpg&h=f72ea0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c823b965ccb7bcf618543aaabf7fb03aaad383e","tid":1350087,"uid":41963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61c498afd50094a431c064b77f9bd0f205ac305c","tid":1350087,"uid":16659,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11664710.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200b/MAIN-Premier-League-Manchester-City-vs-West-Ham-United.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11664710.ece%2